sentences: Roisin Dunne Ross (born 18 September 1965) is an Irish musician.
She is best known for being the replacement guitarist of 7 Year Bitch, after their guitarist Stefanie Sargent died in June 1992.
Ross played on the 7 Year Bitch albums ¡Viva Zapata!
She eventually left the band to pursue other opportunities.
"The History of My Future" b/w "24,900 Miles Per Hour" (promo only) (Atlantic Records, 1996).
